measurements.description: One hundred ten flowers and 19 buds on 18 well-presented staked inflorescences up to 90cm; widest 155cm, foliage spread 65cm, height 110cm, plastic pot 15cm x 30cm, media bark; flowers cupped; sepals and petals white overlaid pink, petals darker distally; lip white, maroon distally, keels yellow; substance firm; texture crystalline; flowers presented fully around the plant.
